data.description: This move-in ready 2 bedroom, 1 bath condo is nestled in a park-like treed setting. Enjoy the community pool and recreation center. Relax or grill year around on your enclosed deck.  Take a stroll in the park to McMenamins Edgfield. Play a round of disc golf, a short walk out your front door. All appliances included. Plenty of storage space, including outdoor locked storage. Bathroom recently updated, and newer floors throughout. Minutes to shopping, dining and brand new athletic center. This location offers both convenience and tranquility and minutes to I-84. Come see this all this amazing opportunity has to offer.
